---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="VTC Le Versoud Airfield (LFLG) | Private Transfer | ShipCars"
    description="Premium VTC service for the Grenoble - Le Versoud airfield (LFLG). Your private driver ensures discreet and punctual transfers to Grenoble, hotels, and ski resorts. Ideal for pilots and business aviation.">

    <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Your <strong>VTC for Le Versoud Airfield</strong> (LFLG)</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">A <strong>private driver</strong> service dedicated to the demands of business and leisure aviation.</p>
            <a href="/en/#booking" class="cta-button">Book my transfer from Le Versoud</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="container text-container">
            <h2>A Tailored Service for the Demands of Private Aviation</h2>
            <p>
                The Grenoble - Le Versoud airfield is a vital hub for <strong>business aviation</strong>, <strong>private pilots</strong>, and gliding enthusiasts. Aware that public transport is unsuitable for this location, ShipCars offers a high-end VTC service ensuring absolute <strong>punctuality</strong> and <strong>flexibility</strong>, essential for meeting a flight plan or a tight professional schedule.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Why Pilots and Passengers Choose ShipCars at Le Versoud</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">ü§´</div>
                    <h3><strong>Discretion</strong> and Professionalism</h3>
                    <p>
                        We understand our clients' need for confidentiality. Your <strong>female driver</strong> ensures absolute discretion, from your pickup at the aircraft to your final destination. <a href="/en/about"><strong>A trusted service</strong></a>.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">üîÑ</div>
                    <h3>Total <strong>Flexibility</strong> for Your Flights</h3>
                    <p>
                        A flight plan can change. We adapt to your schedule, even with last-minute modifications. We ensure your pickup at any time so you can focus on your flight.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">‚ö°Ô∏è</div>
                    <h3>Comfort and Silence to Rest</h3>
                    <p>
                        After a flight, enjoy the silence and comfort of our <a href="/en/vehicle"><strong>100% electric vehicle</strong></a>. An ideal space to work or relax before or after piloting.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Frequent Routes from Le Versoud Airfield</h2>
            <p class="text-container" style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                We cover all your trips to and from the airfield. These are our most requested destinations by private aviation pilots and passengers.
            </p>
            <div class="destinations-grid">
                <div class="dest-card">
                    <h4>Grenoble Center & Hotels</h4>
                    <p>Quickly reach Grenoble city center, your hotel, or your offices.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="dest-card">
                    <h4>Business Hubs (Inovall√©e)</h4>
                    <p>Direct transfers to the region's main business and technology centers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="dest-card">
                    <h4>Ski Resorts</h4>
                    <p>Extend your journey to the Alpine resorts (Courchevel, M√©ribel, Alpe d'Huez...).</p>
                </div>
                 <div class="dest-card">
                    <h4>Other Airports</h4>
                    <p>We also provide connections to Lyon, Grenoble, or Geneva airports.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/en/airport-transfers" class="secondary-button">Back to the airport transfers page</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Arrange Your <strong>Ground Transportation</strong> with Total Simplicity</h2>
            <a href="/en/#booking" class="cta-button">Book my VTC for Le Versoud</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    :root { 
        --accent: #35c2b5; 
        --dark-bg: #2d3a4c;
        --light-bg: #f8f9fa;
        --text-color: #333;
    }
    .page-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542317163-f29e18b570e2?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        color: white;
        padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .page-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2em, 5vw, 3.5em); text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7); }
    .page-hero .subtitle { font-size: 1.2em; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 700px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem auto; }
    
    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
        background-color: var(--accent); 
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px; 
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .secondary-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
        border: 2px solid var(--dark-bg);
        color: var(--dark-bg);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .secondary-button:hover {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        color: white;
    }

    .content-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .text-container { max-width: 800px; text-align: center; margin: 0 auto; }
    .text-container h2, .section-title { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--dark-bg); text-align: center; font-size: 2.2em; }
    .text-container p { font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7; color: #555; }

    .features-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .features-section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
    
    .feature-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        text-align: center;
    }
    .feature-card .icon { font-size: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .feature-card h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--dark-bg); }
    .feature-card p { color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }
    .feature-card a { font-weight: bold; }

    .destinations-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .dest-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent);
    }
    .dest-card h4 { 
        font-size: 1.3em; 
        color: var(--dark-bg);
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem; 
    }
    .dest-card p { 
        color: #666; 
        line-height: 1.6; 
        font-size: 0.95em;
    }

    .cta-section {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        color: white;
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-section h2 { color: white; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

    .bg-light { background-color: var(--light-bg); }
    .text-center { text-align: center; }
    .mt-4 { margin-top: 2rem; }
</style>